cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper presents a deep learning framework for left atrial segmentation in GE-MRI images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) domains. The proposed method also involves multi-task learning, which can be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper involves medical imaging, which can be classified under multimedia (cs.MM).
